N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6055.6 - NCIC Register

State Regulations
DCJS Statewide Register is linked with the NCIC National

Register in Washington. All DCJS Register entries, inquiries and cancellations
will be automatically transmitted to the NCIC Register and will be processed
consistent with NCIC procedures. Notes
